OL,3,CEx-employees speak out as businesses
OL,4,Cstill owed thousands by events company
OL,6,FFormer staff of a company that hosts
OL,7,Fawards ceremonies have spoken out
OL,8,Fafter Welsh businesses were left
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds out of pocket.
OL,11,FITV Cymru Wales previously reported
OL,12,Fthat the event company, 'Oceanic
OL,13,FAwards', had been accused by ticket
OL,14,Fholders of ignoring refund requests,
OL,15,Fleaving business owners frustrated.
OL,17,FWe have spoken to over 25 businesses
OL,18,Fwho bought tickets to a range of
OL,19,Fdifferent events that were postponed
OL,20,For cancelled - leaving them thousands
OL,21,Fof pounds in debt.
