OL,6,FOne owner has even told us they were
OL,7,Fnominated for an award even though
OL,8,Ftheir business had closed down.
OL,10,FOceanic Awards delivers awards
OL,11,Fthroughout the UK and Ireland every
OL,12,Fyear and say, over the past 13 years,
OL,13,Fthey have hosted around 100 events of
OL,14,Fthis kind in Wales - celebrating
OL,15,Findividuals and businesses across
OL,16,Fbeauty, food, wedding, hospitality and
OL,17,Fwomen's sectors.
OL,19,FThe events are run through one of
OL,20,Fseveral companies linked to the
OL,21,FOceanic Group.
