OL,3,CEx-employees speak out as businesses
OL,4,Cstill owed thousands by events company
OL,6,FWe approached Oceanic Awards to
OL,7,Fclarify which company was responsible
OL,8,Ffor holding the customers' money, but
OL,9,Fwe were not provide with an answer.
OL,11,FMore than two years ago, owners of
OL,12,FCwmbran vegan restaurant 'The Queen
OL,13,FInn' purchased ten tickets to attend
OL,14,Fthe Welsh Restaurant Awards. Just days
OL,15,Fbefore the event, the ceremony was
OL,16,Fpostponed and later cancelled
OL,17,Faltogether, with winners announced
OL,18,Fonline instead.
