OL,3,CEx-employees speak out as businesses
OL,4,Cstill owed thousands by events company
OL,6,FDespite repeated assurances, business
OL,7,Fowners Gareth and Jane say they are
OL,8,Fyet to receive their refund of over
OL,9,F#700.
OL,11,F"I was emailing them asking when I'd
OL,12,Fget the refund. They kept saying 'send
OL,13,Fyour bank details and it will be
OL,14,Fprocessed'. I was chasing every two or
OL,15,Fthree weeks and getting the same
OL,16,Fresponse.
OL,18,F"At one point they told me another
OL,19,Fevent was coming up and refunds would
OL,20,Fbe paid once that started making
OL,21,Fmoney."
