OL,4,Cstill owed thousands by events company
OL,6,FCafe proprietor Sara Turner also lost
OL,7,Fmoney after an awards ceremony she had
OL,8,Fpaid to attend was postponed twice.
OL,10,FBy the time the event eventually went
OL,11,Fahead, her business - Green Island
OL,12,FBistro - had closed.
OL,14,FShe continued to chase the company,
OL,15,Fbut is yet to receive the refund she
OL,16,Fwas promised.
