OL,3,CEx-employees speak out as businesses
OL,4,Cstill owed thousands by events company
OL,6,FMonths later, Ms Turner was contacted
OL,7,Fagain by the same awards company,
OL,8,FOceanic Awards, informing her that
OL,9,FGreen Island Bistro had been nominated
OL,10,Ffor Best Cafe 2025.
OL,12,F"The business closed in 2024, so I
OL,13,Fquestioned how that was possible," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"They told me it was customer
OL,17,Fnominations, but how can customers
OL,18,Fvote for a business that isn't open?
OL,19,FIt made me realise the awards aren't
OL,20,Fas realistic as you're led to believe."
