OL,3,CEx-employees speak out as businesses
OL,4,Cstill owed thousands by events company
OL,6,FNow, ex-employees have spoken out
OL,7,Fabout their time working for the
OL,8,FGlasgow based company.
OL,10,FSpeaking anonymously to ITV Wales'
OL,11,FConsumer Affairs reporter Kate Lewis,
OL,12,Fone ex-employee explained their
OL,13,Fexperience of the nomination process:
OL,15,F"The bigger the table you bought and
OL,16,Fthe amount of people you had on the
OL,17,Ftable... I think was the reason for
OL,18,Fyou winning if I'm honest.
