OL,6,F"That's what I saw. So if you had a
OL,7,Ftable of 10 people you were more
OL,8,Flikely to win and if you had 20 people
OL,9,Fon two tables you'd win. Yeah, it was
OL,10,Fnever anything about nominations. I
OL,11,Factually don't believe that was a
OL,12,Fthing if I'm honest.
OL,14,F"I think some people did nominate
OL,15,Fdon't get me wrong but I think if
OL,16,Fcertain categories were looking a bit
OL,17,Fless they would just add people in."
