OL,3,CEx-employees speak out as businesses
OL,4,Cstill owed thousands by events company
OL,6,FThe former employee also told ITV
OL,7,FWales they spoke directly to many of
OL,8,Fthe businesses contacting the company
OL,9,Ffor refunds.
OL,11,F"We were told by management that we
OL,12,Fwere to just keep saying it, keep
OL,13,Fsaying it and that refunds will come,
OL,14,Fbut obviously we knew they weren't
OL,15,Fcoming as it had been like months now
OL,16,Fat this point where people were still
OL,17,Fcalling saying they hadn't received
OL,18,Ftheir refunds."
OL,20,FMore than a dozen former workers have
OL,21,Fbacked up these allegations.
