OL,6,FThe company hit back at claims made by
OL,7,Fformer staff, labelling them as
OL,8,F"bogus" and "seriously misinformed."
OL,10,FThe company defended its awards
OL,11,Fprocess, stating their awards are
OL,12,Fbased on public votes and evidence,
OL,13,Fnoting they process hundreds of
OL,14,Fthousands of votes every year.
OL,16,FThey also pointed to their charitable
OL,17,Fhistory, stating they have raised
OL,18,Fnearly #1 million for various causes.
